      <!-- 1.3 -->
      <h3 id="save_and_cancel_changes">Save and Cancel Changes</h3>

      <!-- 1.3.1 -->
      <h5>Save Changes</h5>
      <p>
        1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Once you change the object you want, click on the save button to keep all changes made in your room.</br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>

      <!-- 1.3.2 -->
      <h5>Cancel Changes</h5>
      <p>
        2.&nbsp&nbsp;Click "cancel changes" button if you don't want to keep any changes made to your room</br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>*Note: you can change multiple objects and save all the changes once you are done.</em></br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>

      <!-- 1.4 -->
      <h3 id="add_and_remove_objects">Add and Remove Objects</h3>

      <!-- 1.4.1 -->
      <h5>Remove Object</h5>
      <p>
        1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Click the edit button on the toolbar and rollover an object you want to remove, then click on the</br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;trash icon to delete.</br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>*Note: Removing this object does not delete its contents. All your bookmarks will be restored if you decide to add the object.</em></br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>

      <!-- 1.4.2 -->
      <h5>Add Object</h5>
      <p>
        2.&nbsp;&nbsp;To add the object back, click on the edit button and the deleted object will appear greyed out with</br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;plus sign (click on it to add the object back to your room)</br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>

      <!-- 2 -->
      <h1>Organize</h1>

      <!-- 2.1 -->
      <h3 id="discover_bookmarks">Discover Bookmarks</h3>
      <p>
        1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Click on any object to open up the bookmark interface</br>
        2.&nbsp;&nbsp;Click on Discover to view all the available sites we have for that category (click to preview the site)</br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>

      <!-- 2.2 -->
      <h3 id="add_and_create_bookmarks">Add and Create Bookmarks</h3>
      <p>
        1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Click on the plus (add icon) on the top right corner to save bookmarks to your selected category.</br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Checkmark icon signifies that it has been added.</br>
        2.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you can't find a site in our library, you have the option to add your own bookmark.</br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>


      <!-- 2.3 -->
      <h3 id="delete_bookmarks">Delete Bookmarks</h3>
      <p>
        1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Go to My Bookmarks tab and to delete a bookmark simply click on the trashbox button on</br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;the top right corner.</br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>


      <!-- 2.4 -->
      <h3 id="active_sites">Active Sites</h3>
      <p>
        1.&nbsp;&nbsp;To view all your active sites click on the star icon on your toolbar.</br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>


      <!-- 3 -->
      <h1>Share</h1>


      <!-- 3.1 -->
      <h3 id="key_requests">Key Requests</h3>
      <p>
        1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Click on the social icon in the toolbar to open up the social interface</br>
        2.&nbsp;&nbsp;Click on Key Request tab</br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>*Note: You will get a red notification when you have a key request pending</em></br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>


      <!-- 3.2 -->
      <h3 id="friends_room">Friend's Room</h3>

      <!-- 3.2.1 -->
      <h5>View Room</h5>
      <p>
        1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Click on the gear icon to view your friend's room</br>
        2.&nbsp;&nbsp;Once in the room you can click on the objects to view your friend's bookmarks and more.</br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>


      <!-- 3.2.2 -->
      <h5>View profile info and photos</h5>
      <p>
        1.&nbsp;&nbsp;Once in the friend's tab click on friend's name or picture to open up their profile page</br>
        2.&nbsp;&nbsp;View and like photos</br>
      </p>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
      </div>
      </br>
      <div>
        <img src="//app.divshot.com/img/placeholder-100x100.gif">
